[p 
	[em 
		"World of Goo
	]em
	" is a physics-based puzzle game for the Wii.  You create structures out of goo and usher around goo balls with them.  The gameplay can be pretty interesting, with quite a few different kinds of goo to play with and some interesting puzzle physics to go with it.
	$LF
]p
